column2: SELECT u.up_col0 as col0, &&&&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z, s.specObjID, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberID, s.z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID ORDER by x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
